{"word":"G1259 - διαλλάσσω - diallássō - dee-al-las'-so - Reconcile","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαλλάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diallássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-al-las'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Reconcile</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒப்புரவாகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to change"},{"paragraph":"2. to change the mind of anyone, to reconcile"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G236 - ἀλλάσσω - allássō - al-las'-so/236\">G236</a>; to <i>change thoroughly</i>, that is, (mentally) to <i>conciliate:</i> - reconcile.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1259/1259\">G1259</a>, <a href=\"#/G236/236\">G236</a>, <a href=\"#/G2643/2643\">G2643</a>, <a href=\"#/G2644/2644\">G2644</a>, <a href=\"#/G3337/3337\">G3337</a>, <a href=\"#/G465/465\">G465</a>, <a href=\"#/G525/525\">G525</a>, <a href=\"#/G604/604\">G604</a>"}]}